AGT Governance plugin for Claude Code
=====================================

This plugin is an independent integration. It is not affiliated with,
endorsed by, or supported by Microsoft or Anthropic.

It packages and adapts components of Microsoft's Agent Governance Toolkit
(AGT) so they run as a Claude Code plugin.

Upstream project
----------------
  Microsoft Agent Governance Toolkit
  https://github.com/microsoft/agent-governance-toolkit
