  Vendored from commit: 4b6bda4deec4d235b05b538486314b2eba26c1ff

Components copied verbatim from AGT (MIT headers retained)
---------------------------------------------------------
  scripts/poisoning.mjs    <- agent-governance-copilot-cli .../lib/poisoning.mjs
  scripts/sdk-loader.mjs   <- agent-governance-copilot-cli .../lib/sdk-loader.mjs

Components adapted from AGT (MIT headers retained)
-------------------------------------------------
  scripts/policy.mjs  <- agent-governance-copilot-cli .../lib/policy.mjs
    Adapted for Claude Code's per-event hook model:
    - platform identifier strings changed from "Copilot CLI" to "Claude Code"
      (DEFAULT_AGENT_ID and the first guard-context line);
    - recordAudit() rewritten to persist a cross-process SHA-256 hash chain
      (the upstream in-memory AuditLogger cannot chain across the fresh process
      that Claude Code spawns per hook event, and exposes no load API);
    - the context-poisoning detector is additionally run over mcp__* tool
      arguments in the PreToolUse path.

  config/default-policy.json and config/profiles/*.json are derived from the
  AGT Copilot CLI policy profiles, retargeted to Claude Code tool names, with
  the shell command rules duplicated for the "Bash" and "PowerShell" tools and
  expanded to cover additional bypasses. The upstream recursive-delete regex
  (\brm\b[\s\S]*\b-rf\b) was also corrected — it matched nothing because of a
  word-boundary error.

Vendored SDK
------------
  vendor/agent-governance-sdk/ contains a build of
  @microsoft/agent-governance-sdk (AGT TypeScript SDK, version 3.7.0, MIT)
  together with its runtime dependencies. Each vendored package retains its
  own LICENSE file inside its directory. The AGT SDK is "Public Preview".

